sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server    

    Note right of browser: The browser prevents the page from submitting to the server by e.preventDefault() specified in spa.js. clicking on the save button makes the browser create a new note and with redrawNotes() add the new note to the page and then make a POST HTTP request to /new_note_spa with the new note value to add the new note in the server

    browser->>server: POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa
    activate server
    server-->>browser: JSON (a message about the status of note creation)
    deactivate server
